                                                           (C) BY BITBUSTER

     THE FIRST TIME EVER IN THE HISTORY OF THE SCENE THE -NEXUS- PARTY
     WILL BE TAKING PLACE IN THE "STADTHALLE DUEREN" IN (GUESS WHERE?)
              DUEREN ! AT THE 20TH OF MAY 1995 !!!!!!!!!!!
                   AND ITS GONNA BE ## BIGGGGGGG ## !!!


+---------+
| TIME &  |
| PLACE   |
+---------+----------------------------------------------------------------
THE WHOLE PARTY WILL BE TAKING PLACE IN THE "STADTHALLE DUEREN".
DUEREN IS A KEWL CITY NEAR AACHEN, WHICH IS NEAR COLGOGNE, WHICH IS IN
"NORDRHEIN WESTFALEN" WHICH IS IN GERMANY, WHICH IS ON EARTH WHICH IS...

IF YOU`RE PLANNING TO TRAVEL BY TRAIN YOU CAN REACH THE PARTYPLACE BY
E.G. FIRST TAKING A TRAIN TO COLOGNE AND THEN SIMPLY BUYING A TICKET
TO DUEREN. WHEN YOU ARRIVE IN DUEREN JUST ASK ANYBODY FOR THE
"STADTHALLE"...(THE "STADTHALLE" IS ABOUT 300 METERS AWAY FROM
THE TRAIN STATION...

IF YOU WANT TO TRAVEL BY CAR JUST SIMPLY TAKE THE FREEWAY FROM
COLOGNE TO AACHEN (A4) AND TAKE THE EXIT "DUEREN". THEN SIMPLY TURN
LEFT AND THERE YOU ARE. JUST FOLLOW THE "SCHOELLERSTRASSE".
AND TURN RIGHT TO THE "BISSMARCKSTRASSE" (ABOUT THE 5TH EXIT)
THE "STADTHALLE" IS ABOUT 300M AWAY ON THE RIGHT HAND SIDE.

(IF YOU HAVE PROBLEMS GETTING TO THE PARTY JUST WRITE TO US OR CALL
THE HOTLINE !)

ANYWAY... WE WILL HANG UP LOTS OF NEXUS-SIGNS. STARTING FROM THE FREEWAY
EXIT!

THEN PARK YOUR CAR AND GO TO THE FRONT DOOR. THE DOORS WILL BE OPEN
AT ABOUT 6.00PM !

