+----------+
|   THE    |
|PARTYPLACE|
+----------+---------------------------------------------------------------
- THE STADTHALLE CAN HOLD UP TO 1800 PEOPLE. IN THE MAIN HALL THERE WILL
  BE A _BIG_ PARTY WITH 70.000 WATTS MINDBLASTING LIGHT AND LASER-EFFECTS,
  AND A 12.000 WATTS SOUND EQUIPMENT! SO BE READY TO DANCE !

  ALL KINDS OF MUSIC WILL BE PLAYED BY LOCAL TOP-DJs FROM TEKKNO TO HOUSE,
  FROM ROCK TO HIP HOP AND FROM CROSSOVER TO DANCEFLOOR ! EVERYTHING YOU
  WANT ! (WE WILL ALSO HAVE A SPECIAL LIVE-GIG FROM A FAMOUS TEKKNO-DJ !
  SORRY... WE CANT SAY MORE...ITS GONNA BE A SURPRISE !)

- WE WILL HAVE OUR OWN COMPETITION-ROOM TO RELAX AND SMALL TALK.
  ON THE 4 X 4 METERS GIANT SCREEN WE WILL SHOW THE BEST DEMOS FROM
  THE LAST 10 YEARS AND ALSO SOME ANIME-MOVIES...(IF YOU HAVE SOMETHING
  YOU WANT SHOW TO THE PUBLIC CROW (FOR EXAMPLE A KEWL VIDEO PRODUCTION
  OR WHAT ELSE...) JUST HAND IT TO ONE OF THE ORGANIZERS!
  WE WILL BE GLAD TO SHOW IT ON THE SCREEN...

- FOR DA PAINT-MANIACS OF YOU WE WILL HAVE A BIGGGG GRAFITTI-WALL INSIDE !
  BUT DO ONLY DRAW ON _THIS_ WALL ! (SORRY NO SPRAYCANS !)

- AT ABOUT 10.00 PM WE WILL START WITH THE COMPETITIONS ! THE DEADLINE IS
  AT 9.00 PM !!!
  ALL COMPETITIONS AND OTHER ACTIVITIES WILL BE HELD IN OUR COMPETITION
  ROOM! YOU ALSO  _CAN_ BRING OUR COMPUTERS IF YOU WANT...
  BUT DONT BE TOO LATE ! ->IF ITS GETTING TOO FULL WE WILL NOT ACCEPT
  ANY COMPUTERS ANYMORE.

  DO IMPORTANT THINGS FOR EXAMPLE FINISHING YOUR DEMO/GFX/MODULE...AND DONT FORGET TO BRING YOUR
  OWN POWER CABLES !
  (IF ITS GETTING TOO FULL - BAD LUCK FOR YOUR COMPUTER :-))

- A PROFESSIONAL 10-MEN STRONG SECURITY-TEAM WILL BE RUNNING AROUND
  TO KEEP YOU SAFE !

- IF YOU`RE GETTING HUNGRY YOU`LL HAVE THE BIG CHOICE: A LOT OF
  CHEAP FASTFOOD RESTAURANTS, CAFES, CHINESE, GREECE AND TURKEY
  SNACK BARS ARE IN THE NEAR SURROUNDING OF 200 METERS !

PRICES AT THE PARTYPLACE:
-------------------------

THE ENTRY FEE IS 10DM AT THE MAIN ENTRY (WHICH _WE_ DONT GET !)
AND 10DM (WHICH -WE- GET!(FOR THE COMPETITIONS))

ALL PRICES FOR DRINKS WILL BE LOW
(ABOUT 2,50.-DM FOR A 0,33 BEER OR COKE !)

