P*L*U*S: MANY COMMERCIAL GAMES AND HARDWARE LIKE SOUNDCARDS ETC...
--------

COMPETITION RULEZ:
------------------
- THE AMIGA DEMO & INTRO MUST BE RUNABLE ON A STANDART A1200/020/14MHZ
  OR A A1200 WITH 030/50MHZ OR A A4000/040/25MHZ !
  IT DOESNT MATTER IF ITS A EXE OR A SELF-BOOTING DEMO !

- THE PC-DEMO AND INTRO MUST BE RUNABLE ON A STANDART
  486/66 WITH 4MB AND GUS MAX (512 K) OR SOUNDBLASTER !

- IF YOU HAVE A DEMO FOR THE WILD COMPO YOU SHOULD BRING YOUR OWN
  EQUIPMENT WHICH WAS USED TO MAKE IT !

- THE MODULE MUST BE IN NORMAL PROTRACKER OR SCREAMTRACKER FORMAT !
  WE WILL NOT ACCEPT ANY MODULES, THAT ARE BIGGER THAN 1 MB !

- THE PICTURES MUST BE IN ILBM(IFF) OR GIF FORMAT !
  EVERYTHING UP TO TRUECOLOR IS ALLOWED...
  (!!!_NO_SCANS !!!)

- EACH GROUP CAN PARTICIPATE WITH ONE DEMO OR INTRO

- THE DEMO OR INTRO SHOULD NOT YET BE RELEASED AT ANY TIME BEFORE
- (THE DEMO WILL BE RELEASED AT THE PARTY !)

- ALL CONTRIBUTIONS FOR THE COMPETITIONS MUST BE HANDED TO THE ORGANIZERS
  *BEFORE* 9.00 PM !!!


+---------+
|THE RULEZ|
+---------+----------------------------------------------------------------
OR: THINGS TO KEEP IN MIND!

- YOU ARE NOT ALLOWED TO BRING YOUR OWN FOOD, DRINKS OR ANY OTHER KIND
  OF DRUGS... SO LEAVE THEM AT HOME OR TAKE THEM OUTSIDE ! :-)
  (THE SECURITY TEAM WILL CHECK EACH PERSON AT THE ENTRY !!!)

- RACIST SIGNS AND BEHAVIOUR WILL NOT BE TOLERATED ! (KICKED OUT :-)

- PERSONS USING OR SELLING HARD DRUGS OR CAUSE ANY KIND OF TROUBLE
  (FIGHTING, STEALING OR WHAT ELSE) WILL BE HANDED OVER TO THE POLICE !

- WE ARE NOT IN ANY WAY RESPONSIBLE FOR THE LOSS OF ANY PERSONAL
  BELONGINGS! (SO KEEP AN EYE ON YOUR COMPUTER !) :-)

